{"tid":691832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓媒︰金正恩要求特朗普投資元山賭場","createTime":"2018-06-06T05:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T19:16:18.000Z","uid":54870,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"eac8a5cd19c3c9e6bb4ae756747d8dc66f607405","tid":691832,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"南韓傳媒報道，北韓領袖金正恩「心腹」、統一戰線部部長金英哲日前在白宮與美國總統特朗普見面時，傳達金正恩的口訊，希望美國可以在北韓投資協助在元山、馬息嶺一帶發展賭場等觀光事業。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《東亞日報》報道，金英哲向特朗普轉達金正恩的口訊，指北韓同意特朗普提出徹底、迅速非核化進程，因此在「特金會」前一周，雙方可就有關議題細節加快協商。<br />\n消息指，北韓正向美國作出試探，希望美國會補償北韓非核化措施，並分階段放寬制裁。消息又指，金英哲在白宮會談中，具體提到建造元山賭場、增設馬息嶺滑雪場等事宜。<br />\n「元山葛麻海岸觀光地區」是金正恩在1月新年賀詞中公佈的計劃，是重點事業之一。南韓政府預測，若北韓在元山建成賭場，經營國際旅遊園區，每年可以創造約5000萬美元(3.9億港元)收益；而北韓的年均貿易額為70億至80億美元(546至624億港元)，數額可觀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180606/58279404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58279404&d=iSVeGoN7CwIAGDQczWzVlzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f74bc159\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58279404&h=23fdd135\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180606/58279404</a>"},{"pid":"d5c86b48ae0b87ed4d9421a0dfb6fd373425315c","tid":691832,"uid":32938,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"贏錢出唔返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dde03ce296d467f97a736a6459000c5e1374d7","tid":691832,"uid":7699,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開賭一定賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji